{"tid":2497177,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"尚德邨獨居婦離世後半月　走廊仍留屍臭　住戶轟房署愛理不理","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T12:26:01.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"512e72a0bb881f272867934fbf0aab1e518bbdc1","tid":2497177,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JCoxxOAFt3ZdWLqAjUCeR9qgi8I=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M7UANFJPUZDXHNS4KXXEOS4XFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJCoxxOAFt3ZdWLqAjUCeR9qgi8I%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM7UANFJPUZDXHNS4KXXEOS4XFU.jpg&h=db718ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁先生指臭氣難忍，每次出入都需要用浸過滴露消毒藥水的濕毛巾掩鼻而行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uMrDa7zrmpnNVMaH2FHvWPlKOKI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3DFD2Q7AURFOFMCETOIPN36KPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuMrDa7zrmpnNVMaH2FHvWPlKOKI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3DFD2Q7AURFOFMCETOIPN36KPM.jpg&h=097a1ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事單位門外放置多個空氣清新劑及臭丸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dydo5VD-lgAeLX1dfJkuqAx403o=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GKPBHEM72FBPHMXUH2PZ55HQCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fdydo5VD-lgAeLX1dfJkuqAx403o%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGKPBHEM72FBPHMXUH2PZ55HQCI.jpg&h=fc679d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁先生指房署和警方對事件愛理不理，狠批兩個部門互相卸責：「好官僚主義，佢哋感受唔到我哋嗰陣壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n一名獨居於尚德邨的老婦早前倒斃單位內，屍體雖然已經移走半個月，但屍臭仍充斥整個樓層及走廊，令鄰居相當困擾。房署雖然於涉事單位外放置防臭丸辟臭，但當局回覆區議員的查詢時表示，需待警方搜證及親屬認領財物後，才可安排清潔人員。有居民難抵臭味，只能用浸過滴露的濕毛巾掩鼻而行，甚至到酒店暫住數天避臭，批評政府部門互相推卸責任，態度愛理不理。<br />\n<br />\n當區區議員李嘉睿其後指，房署稱警方需待親屬認領財物及搜證，才會進行單位清潔，令梁先生非常不滿，認為政府部門互相推卸責任，棄市民生活於不顧：「好官僚主義，佢哋感受唔到我哋嗰陣壓力，如果5分滿分，我剩係畀0.5分，（房署）剩係封板根本無處理過（問題）」。他更透露，女兒擔心夏季將至，若屍臭問題一直未解決，可能滋生細菌。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210420/M4J24TNKGJAYJLCZY6UTMA4QLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210420%2FM4J24TNKGJAYJLCZY6UTMA4QLY%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=6fbecbcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210420%2FM4J24TNKGJAYJLCZY6UTMA4QLY%2F&h=e63ef27b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210420/M4J24TNKGJAYJLCZY6UTMA4QLY/</a>"},{"pid":"5950c0bc919159633451f906d8f4461738a717c7","tid":2497177,"uid":107231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會有癲佬因為咁燒左個單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350147bbe9856c5e15800b1466a4869487cde203","tid":2497177,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"好臭嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d6f58eae444dc4f357d3675f810437e47b02e0","tid":2497177,"uid":197386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"350147bbe9856c5e15800b1466a4869487cde203","tid":2497177,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"好臭嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"未唔聞過人既 但聞過死老鼠味<br />\n死一隻都好大味<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgm